thread.title: Adult coloring night offered

title: Adult coloring night offered
text:
Adult coloring night offered 0 comments 
CORUNNA — The Corunna Branch of the Community District Library will host a program for adults from 6 to 7:30 p.m. Oct. 27. 
Coloring isn’t just for kids anymore, library staff said in a press release. “Invite a friend or make a new one while coloring and visiting at the library.
